Normalisation

mi1 = min(ou$OU_LOS_hrs)
ma1 = max(ou$OU_LOS_hrs)
ou$OU_LOS_hrs = (ou$OU_LOS_hrs - mi1)/(ma1 - mi1)

mi2 = min(ou$BloodPressureUpper)
ma2 = max(ou$BloodPressureUpper)
ou$BloodPressureUpper = (ou$BloodPressureUpper - mi2)/(ma2 - mi2)

mi3 = min(ou$BloodPressureLower)
ma3 = max(ou$BloodPressureLower)
ou$BloodPressureLower = (ou$BloodPressureLower - mi3)/(ma3 - mi3)

mi4 = min(ou$BloodPressureDiff)
ma4 = max(ou$BloodPressureDiff)
ou$BloodPressureDiff = (ou$BloodPressureDiff - mi4)/(ma4 - mi4)

mi5 = min(ou$Pulse)
ma5 = max(ou$Pulse)
ou$Pulse = (ou$Pulse - mi5)/(ma5 - mi5)

mi6 = min(ou$PulseOximetry)
ma6 = max(ou$PulseOximetry)
ou$PulseOximetry = (ou$PulseOximetry - mi6)/(ma6 - mi6)

mi7 = min(ou$Respirations)
ma7 = max(ou$Respirations)
ou$Respirations = (ou$Respirations - mi7)/(ma7 - mi7)

mi8 = min(ou$Temperature)
ma8 = max(ou$Temperature)
ou$Temperature = (ou$Temperature - mi8)/(ma8 - mi8)

mi9 = min(ou$Age)
ma9 = max(ou$Age)
ou$Age = (ou$Age - mi9)/(ma9 - mi9)
